{"word":"G138 - αἱρέομαι - hairéomai - hahee-reh'-om-ahee - Choose","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αἱρέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hairéomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hahee-reh'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Choose"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தெரிந்துகொள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to take, to take for oneself, to choose, prefer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably akin to <a href=\"#/G142 - αἴρω - aírō - ah'-ee-ro/142\">G142</a>; to <i>take for oneself</i>, that is, to <i>prefer</i>. Some of the forms are borrowed from a cognate (<b>&#x03B5;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;</b> h<b>ellomai</b>), which is otherwise obsolete: - choose. Some of the forms are borrowed from a cognate hellomai, hel-lom-ahee; which is otherwise obsolete."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1243 - διαίρεσις - diaíresis - dee-ah'-ee-res-is/1243\">G1243</a>, <a href=\"#/G1244 - διαιρέω - diairéō - dee-ahee-reh'-o/1244\">G1244</a>, <a href=\"#/G138 - αἱρέομαι - hairéomai - hahee-reh'-om-ahee/138\">G138</a>, <a href=\"#/G139 - αἵρεσις - haíresis - hah'-ee-res-is/139\">G139</a>, <a href=\"#/G140 - αἱρετίζω - hairetízō - hahee-ret-id'-zo/140\">G140</a>, <a href=\"#/G141 - αἱρετικός - hairetikós - hahee-ret-ee-kos'/141\">G141</a>"}]}